          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-1607346849428-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips are almost done, remove the tray from the oven and sprinkle over your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – these are your <strong>chilli chips</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche buns</strong> in half, then add to the tray with the chips and return to the oven for 3-4 min or until the brioche is warmed through and toasted</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1607346895578-x200.jpg",
